7) Integration with your stack

* PSD → use P7 (triangulation) + Gates 2–3
* RDRH → run P1 (mechanism stress) at Δ and P5 at R₁
* Kintsugi → P8 before promotion
* ZPC/Reversibility → ensure R3 on probes you intend to act on

⸻

8) Clean Compression

Don’t brute-force.
Cover the axes, score hard, keep only what survives repetition and transfer.

